videos.headline: Gaskin puts Huskies on the board first
videos.description: Myles Gaskin rushes for a 2-yard touchdown to give Washington an early lead.

videos.headline: Stanford ties it with a Love TD
videos.description: Bryce Love runs for a 1-yard touchdown to tie the game in the second.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Stanford ties it with a Love TD) 2017/11/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gaskin 2-for-2 on Washington TDs
videos.description: Myles Gaskin rushes for 15 yards for his second and the Huskies' second touchdown.

videos.headline: Love puts Stanford ahead
videos.description: Bryce Love breaks through the middle for a 13-yard Cardinal touchdown in the third quarter.

videos.headline: Gaskin fumbles early in fourth quarter
videos.description: Myles Gaskin fumbles on the Washington 31 and is recovered by Stanford's Dylan Jackson.

videos.headline: Love's third TD pads Stanford's lead
videos.description: Bryce Love rushes for a 9-yard touchdown giving the Cardinals a steady lead.

videos.headline: Gaskin gets third TD of the day
videos.description: Myles Gaskin rushes for a 1-yard touchdown to close the gap on Stanford.
